      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "Wit et al. reported no graft displacement and postulated that sutureless and glue free graft resulted in even tension across the whole graft interface The mean operative time ± SD was 26.3±1.41 minutes (Range: 24-28 minutes), and the mean graft fixation time ± SD was 11.5±1.82 minutes (Range: 9-14 minutes).These durationsare comparable but longer than other studies Our results confirmed significantly lower postoperative signs and symptoms including irritation,pain, foreign body sensation, photophobia, hyperemia and chemosis at all follow up visits."
